**Featured Breeder**
Onesta Cane Corsowww.onestacanecorso.com





​We love all of your Bloom products!! Onesta is proud of our Cane Corsos, Apollo (pictured in the first slide show) is 145 pounds, is very active, muscular, and obedient. 
 




 



​Nutrition is a huge part of our puppy program. We use Bloom Supplements every day for our Cane Corsos and all our new puppies. We encourage all of our puppies new families to use Bloom Supplements also. We take time out with each new family to educate them why Bloom Supplements are so important in the growth and health of their new puppy. 
We love to support each new family and make sure they understand how to provide the best care and health for their puppy. We like to call ourselves a lifetime support system to all of our new puppy owners. We are here to answer questions, concerns, or if they just would like to share new pictures and we love to hear about their experiences!!




You can become a **Featured Breeder** by sending us a picture of your Bloom Animal  & tell us why you use Bloom Supplements.








