 BloomSky | Introducing the BloomSky Storm 


























                SKY2 + STORM
            

                The first community-based weather camera station
                to share your BloomSky story.
            






SKY2
Same Look, New Experience.

                    The updated 5 in 1 weather
                    camera station accurately measures
                    Temperature, Humidity, Barometric
                    Pressure and Precipitation.
                

                    New Feature:
                    Bluetooth enabled for easy setup.
                







STORM
New Device, More Data.

                    High precision 4 in 1 wireless weather
                    device measures real-time UV, Rainfall,
                    Wind Speed & Direction.
                

                    (STORM works with your SKY1 or SKY2 only)
                






SKY2
Read Full Details




HD Camera
Ultra wide angle lens to capture real-time images of the sky





Precipitation
Sensor promptly indicates rainfall





Humidity
Relative humidity precision: ± 3% RH (typ. 10–90% RH), Range of relative humidity: 0-100% RH





Temperature
Operating temperature range: -4°F (-20°C) to 131°F (55°C) Temperature accuracy: ±0.3°C (Max)





Pressure
Absolute pressure range: 300 - 1100 hPa





Charge
Solar powered panel for automatic recharge






STORM
Read Full Details




Rain Collector
Tipping cup accuracy: 0.2 mm per tip, no limit range





Anemometer
Wind speed accuracy: 1 m/s or ±5%  Start-up speed: 0.5 m/s





Wind Direction
Measures direction in 8 compass points





UV Sensor
UV exposure range: 280nm - 400nm (UV-A, UV-B).





Connectivity
Wireless communication range: Up to 100 meters (110 yards)





Charge
Compact solar panel for continuous operation





App-enabled
Sharing on iOS or Android to popular social platforms





Community Integration
Compatible with other weather platforms





Smart Control Ready
IFTTT, Nest, SmartThings, and more







